social_posts.post_text: I don’t think I trust anybody the way I trust @sabrinahabibi with my hair 😌

three years ago I met this wonderful human being, and I knew that I would love and cherish this friendship when we bonded over our love for Taylor Swift and In & Out burger. Fast forward to three years later and plenty of unforgettable memories, I am lucky to call this person one of my best friends ever. Kate, you marvel this world with your generous heart and I’m lucky to be a part of your world. Happy Birthday. You deserve everything amazing. 💗

To Namashi, 
your time has finally arrived. oh god, have I waited so long to say that. from watching you dance around to dad, Govinda & Shahrukh Khan’s songs to now watching you achieve your dream of debuting your first movie on the big screen, I can say without a doubt that I have never met someone who is as hardworking, resilient & talented as you. the drive and hunger you have for the craft is beyond inspiring. I wish I could be there to celebrate with you in person, but my love is pouring out for you from oceans away. you were always meant to be seen through the big screen and I can’t wait to see you there countless times. I am so lucky to have you as my brother.
Bad Boy is out in cinemas this Friday, 28th of April!
